Maximum entropy has also been applied successfully for summarization in the broadcast news domain.Aided summarizationMachine learning techniques from closely related fields such as information retrieval or text mining have been successfully adapted to help automatic summarization.Apart from Fully Automated Summarizers (FAS), there are systems that aid users with the task of summarization (MAHS = Machine Aided Human Summarization), for example by highlighting candidate passages to be included in the summary, and there are systems that depend on post-processing by a human (HAMS = Human Aided Machine Summarization).ApplicationsThere are different types of summaries depending what the summarization program focuses on to make